description:
&lt;p&gt;This post is only open to current employees of University Hospitals of Morecambe Bay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A 7 month Secondment post opportunity has arisen within our Band 3 Radiology Specialist Secretarial team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should have excellent communication skills, organisational skills, administration skills and customer care skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be expected, as part of the team, to ensure Radiology achieves its performance targets and efficiencies as well as ensuring we have an excellent administration service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You would support the Radiology team and be the point of contact for our service users. You would be part of a cross bay team working at the Royal Lancaster Infirmary, although some travel to other sites may be required as part of the post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time 37.5 hour post worked over 5 days, Monday to Friday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anyone newly appointed to the trust will be subject to the completion of a satisfactory 6 month probationary period (this includes bank staff). This will give the new staff member an opportunity to become familiar with the role and working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
